iL6r4xlFUBQ8K1AUw", "profilePicHighQuality": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E03AQG2y134cwXpgQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_200_200/profile-displayphoto-shrink_200_200/0/1516342351087?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=DpyvQ0F9LEJlP80ROm84vLSw9tiL6r4xlFUBQ8K1AUw", "publicIdentifier": "mcgregora", "recommendations/0/context": "Andrew managed Sebastian directly", "recommendations/0/date": "August 22, 2015", "recommendations/0/description": "I employed Sebastian as a member of my concierge Team as a Doorman for the opening of W hong Kong.Sebastian certainly had the charisma, style and fully engages guests with his quick wit and humour.W hong Kong was the first chic lifestyle hotel to open in Hong Kong and Sebastian fulfilled the brief of being a dynamic person we needed to be the face of our hotel.Sebastian was a delight to work with a consummate team player, Fluent in Cantonese,English and Tagalog as well as the gift of the gab. Sebastian is fully able to engage the guest and direct them to their location either inside or outside the hotel. As a manager, I place great importance on employees who have to the confidence to engage my guests as Sebastian always did. Guest feedback on Sebastian's performance proved I made the right choice in hiring Sebastian. Sebastian also completed on the job training within the Concierge and Front office department.", "recommendations/0/name": "Sebastian Alcaraz", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Self Employed", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sebastianalcaraz/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAwpKRoBXO_JIdXBP5ze3DYWfE9S_6HZ4wc", "recommendations/1/context": "Andrew worked with Kevin on the same team", "recommendations/1/date": "January 8, 2014", "recommendations/1/description": "Kevin is truly a can do guy always patient and deals with challenges in a firm and calm manner.. Always solution orientated manager,Kevin could  always be relied upon to get the job done with mimimal fuss and bother ensuring that all operations continued smoothly. An all rounded manager who understood opperations completely ! Kevin could always be relied upon to find the best cost effective solution to any problem. Kevin is communicates well and an extreme pleasure to work with in all aspects of a hotel's operations. I wish him well in his future endeavours !", "recommendations/1/name": "Kevin White", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Director of Engineering and Security at Four Seasons Hotels and Resorts", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kevin-white-165a8185/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABIiV50BPCvpppBiS-dNzq-nqxZ6uVoy2f0", "recommendations/2/context": "Andrew managed Kathy directly", "recommendations/2/date": "June 19, 2012", "recommendations/2/description": "Kathy is a very resourceful Concierge whom I hired to help open the new W Kong. She was very instrumental in helping me set up the department and the Concierge data base. Kathy is extremely customer focused and always willing to learn new things and encourage others to follow suit. Kathy is a natural born leader and an urbane conversationist. Kathy was a breath of fresh air to my team who both took and gave direction well.  Kathy was able to iinsipre her colleagues to achieve a common goal. I would be very happy to recommend Kathy to any future employer for her dedication and willingness to try anything.", "recommendations/2/name": "Kathy Ribeiro", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "“You don’t understand anything until you learn it more than one way”- Marvin Minsky", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kathy-ribeiro-b5813853/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAs7a3QBnSlHIy3V_eGRnKkNzFNX8fQ_z0E", "recommendations/3/context": "Andrew was senior to Ethan but didn't manage Ethan directly", "recommendations/3/date": "September 15, 2011", "recommendations/3/description": "Ethan is always a consummate professional when dealing with guests and staff members alike. A very solution driven manager with a fantastic rapport with colleagues. Always a great sense of humour and willing to do anything to get the job done. Ethan moved to Hong Kong from Singapore for just after opening. A difficult opening but Ethan rose to the very unique challlenges of moving to a new country and new hotel. Ethan was an absolute asset to the front of house team. I would enjoy having the chance to work with Ethan again and would have no hesitation in recommending Ethan as a true and honest hotelier", "recommendations/3/name": "Ethan Pang", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Hospitality | Customer Service and Relations | Social Media Management", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ethanpang/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJ0RyABxn6tEcY8RF4P3vzmCB0WqQYQ5nQ", "recommendations/4/context": "Andrew managed Angela directly", "recommendations/4/date": "December 18, 2010", "recommendations/4/description": "It is a pleasure and an honour to recommend Angela.  I employed Angela to rennovate and re-estabish the business Centre at the Island Shangri-La. Angela was innovative and a great motivator to the team. She handled the renovation with great patience under extreme pressure !! She was influential in ensuring that the business centre turned it's first profit in years !! Angela was always a very urbane conversationlist. Always reliable and always friendly !! Angela would be a great asset to any team.", "recommendations/4/name": "Angela L.", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Talent Development • Talent Management • Learning & Development • Hospitality Industry • Insurance Industry • Customer Service", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/angela-lee-1022/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAASwSJ4BsiAw14la6U3eYVifQ0xgZAg43XY", "recommendations/5/context": "Andrew was senior to Stephen but didn't manage Stephen directly", "recommendations/5/date": "December 4, 2010", "recommendations/5/description": "I 